you exist at all.

709
01:06:20,421 --> 01:06:22,059
Oh, Nick.

710
01:06:25,021 --> 01:06:28,172
I guess l forgive you
for standing me up.

711
01:06:28,621 --> 01:06:31,658
The last thing you want to do
is watch me eat.

712
01:06:34,381 --> 01:06:36,451
So how can l help you?

713
01:06:38,021 --> 01:06:43,015
Open a brokerage account, buy me 2000
shares of a stock called Allied Resources.

714
01:06:52,301 --> 01:06:56,817
-Having seconds?
-Yeah. I suddenly got hungry again.

715
01:06:57,301 --> 01:07:00,452
Must have been all that running
you did this afternoon.

716
01:07:00,621 --> 01:07:02,339
Must be.

717
