737
01:08:27,941 --> 01:08:29,579
Ah, George.

738
01:08:30,061 --> 01:08:33,849
You're the best. This will be the perfect
place for me to get some work done.

739
01:08:34,021 --> 01:08:36,615
I left the number of a good therapist.

740
01:08:36,781 --> 01:08:39,500
If you feel like talking,
she's very understanding.

741
01:08:39,661 --> 01:08:41,856
She's helped Richard a lot.

742
01:08:42,141 --> 01:08:44,132
Thanks, George.

743
01:08:46,221 --> 01:08:48,655
Good to know
Richard's getting some help.

744
01:08:49,861 --> 01:08:53,570
Chuck, it's George.
Wanna hear a hot one?

745
01:08:53,741 --> 01:08:56,460
Guess who broke into my house
and ran up $500. . .

746
01:08:56,621 --> 01:09:00,057
. . .on food and booze on my accounts.
Nick Halloway.

747
01:09:01,381 --> 01:09:03,895
No, he's not dead. He's on a binge.

748
01:09:05,261 --> 01:09:07,900
-This is ridiculous.
-No, it is not.

749
01:09:08,061 --> 01:09:10,495
Just let me finish.
You owe me a meal anyway.

750
01:09:10,661 --> 01:09:14,256
I'm sure you have better things to do,
places to go, people to see.

751
01:09:14,421 --> 01:09:16,935
First of all, l don't have
better things to do.

752
01:09:17,101 --> 01:09:19,695
I'm in between projects right now. . .

753
01:09:20,501 --> 01:09:22,776
. . .and l'm not seeing anybody.

754
01:09:22,941 --> 01:09:25,057
That's an understatement.

755
01:09:27,821 --> 01:09:31,814
It's a hell of a lot more comfortable
than that Ace bandage.

756
01:09:33,181 --> 01:09:35,411
It really works.

757
01:09:36,301 --> 01:09:38,292
Oh, Nick, you have a face again.

758
01:09:39,181 --> 01:09:42,332
If l had eyes and teeth,
l'd be a whole head.

759
01:09:45,701 --> 01:09:47,339
It's nice to see you.

760
01:09:47,981 --> 01:09:50,211
