and get in a cab.

875
01:21:31,181 --> 01:21:32,773
And what about you?

876
01:21:32,941 --> 01:21:35,978
Look out your window at the phone booth
on the corner.

877
01:21:37,861 --> 01:21:39,089
Yeah, l see you.

878
01:21:39,861 --> 01:21:43,649
As soon as l see her out of your building
and in a cab, l give myself up.

879
01:21:43,821 --> 01:21:46,858
